window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Have you heard of the Ultimate Appraiser?</b></p> <p>Melchior was a guy who always wanted to leave home.</p> <p>Then one day, he got his wish and was transported to the world of Maestros. He liked the place, so he took advantage of his cheat-level abilities and settled down there, intent on leading a quiet and profitable life.</p> <p>Time passed.</p> <p>Nowadays, Melchior's a guy who lives under the radar, traveling from place to place, plundering dungeons, making money, and visiting his favorite people. Armed with his completely unfair [Appraisal]<b> </b>ability, no other Appraiser can compare to him. His income is the most secure and certain thing in Maestros.</p> <p>But Maestros is an ever-changing world, one populated by humans blessed by gods themselves, the Masters. Dangerous power and new sources of revenue are always appearing. If it stopped there, Melchior would be happy, but a great shift is on the horizon, one that might actually harm Melchior's business and partners.</p> <p>The forces of fate are moving, but Melchior is the one person they should never oppose, lest he shows them just why he is the Ultimate <i>Cheat </i>Appraiser.</p> <p><i>Isekai Cheat Appraiser: A Slow Life of Wandering &amp; Treasure-Hunting</i> is a new slice-of-life and adventure story of a guy who wants to make and spend money. Here's what you can expect in this series:</p> <ul> <li>Cheat-level abilities</li> <li>Overpowered protagonist</li> <li>Fantastical and abundant romance</li> <li>Dungeon crawling</li> <li>Slice-of-life elements</li> <li>LitRPG elements</li> </ul>"; 
